						               													<description>Card Castle is a fast-paced, slapping card game that puts your reflexes to the test. Out-slap others to win cards and rule the Card Castle! Inspired by traditional card games like War and Slap-Jack, Card Castle adds several new twists including battling armies, tricky look-alikes, powerful Wizards, and fiery dragons.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In more detail, the goal in Card Castle is to out-slap your opponents, win all their cards, and become ruler of the castle. Players take turns flipping cards blindly from the top of their army decks onto the center of the table or playmat. When slappable opportunities present themselves (doubles, doors, or wizards), the first player to slap the pile of cards wins the battle and all the cards in the pile.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But be sure you don't slap the dragon!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
